text: Alexander Falk (born May 24, 1993) is a Swedish ice hockey defenceman. He is currently playing with Södertälje SK of the HockeyAllsvenskan (Allsv). Falk made his Elitserien debut playing with Djurgårdens IF during the 2011–12 Elitserien season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Djurgårdens IF Hockey players Category:Swedish ice hockey defencemen Category:Timrå IK players
